                    <h1 class="domdom">21</h1>

                    <h1>Film: <a href="/on/film/627">Alamar (Mexico) (2009)</a></h1>

                    <h2>21 Nov 2010, 7:30 p.m.</h2>

                    <p>A visual poem in the stunning setting of a little house in the blue Mexican sea, where a father shows his 5 year old boy how to go fishing. Between documentary and fiction, this little gem has won prestigious prizes, among which the highest prize (tiger award) at the Rotterdam Film Festival. </p>

                    <p class="viewlink"><a href="/on/film/627">Read More &raquo;</a></p>

