                    <h1 class="domdom">25</h1>

                    <h1>Film: <a href="/on/film/628">The Dog Pound (La Perrera, Uruguay) (2006)</a></h1>

                    <h2>25 Nov 2010, 7:30 p.m.</h2>

                    <p>Winner of the Best Film Award at the Rotterdam Film Festival, and elected Best Uruguayan Film of 2006 by the country’s Association of Film Critics, this is a slow and contemplative film about David, a 25-year-old who loves smoking pot, and has a heroic capacity for doing nothing. Tragicomedy of a slacker, shot on 16mm.</p>

                    <p class="viewlink"><a href="/on/film/628">Read More &raquo;</a></p>

