                    <h1 class="domdom">28</h1>

                    <h1>Film: <a href="/on/film/584">Whisky (Uruguay) (2003)</a></h1>

                    <h2>28 Nov 2010, 7:30 p.m.</h2>

                    <p>Multi-awarded at some of the most prestigious international film festivals (Cannes, Tokyo, Chicago, Peru, Spain, etc), this is a very subtle film about human communication, or the impossibility of it. The owner of a sock factory asks one of his employees to act as his wife during the visit of his brother.</p>

                    <p class="viewlink"><a href="/on/film/584">Read More &raquo;</a></p>

